<p>If that’s not the issue, please send a link to your code repo.</p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2025-03-25T12:10:31.326Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":72,"readers_count":71,"score":19.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":496835,"topic_slug":"limelight-localization-help","display_username":"Alexander Carlisi","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"","bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":62389,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/limelight-localization-help/496835/4","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3567945,"name":"Tharun","username":"thaMan","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/e5b9ba/{size}.png","created_at":"2025-03-25T13:44:16.490Z","cooked":"<p>We switch the tag as in when we deploy our code we’ll put it in front of a tag and sometimes it’ll end up not rotating or sometimes it’ll end up being inside the reef itself.</p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2025-03-25T13:44:16.490Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":2,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":50,"readers_count":49,"score":10.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":496835,"topic_slug":"limelight-localization-help","display_username":"Tharun","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":65,"username":"Joe_Ross","name":"Joe Ross","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/joe_ross/{size}/37_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":57591,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/limelight-localization-help/496835/5","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null},{"id":3567946,"name":"Tharun","username":"thaMan","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/e5b9ba/{size}.png","created_at":"2025-03-25T13:44:55.261Z","cooked":"<p>I see I think I might want to check again but im pretty sure that when our robot code our gyro resets itself</p>","post_number":6,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2025-03-25T13:44:55.261Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":3,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":49,"readers_count":48,"score":9.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":496835,"topic_slug":"limelight-localization-help","display_username":"Tharun","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":true,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":24594,"username":"SLAB-Mr.Thomas","name":"SLAB-Mr.Thomas","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/www.chiefdelphi.com/slab-mr.thomas/{size}/182153_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":57591,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_